                        <interp inst="t18510707-1506-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 31.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The prisoner was further charged with having before been convicted: to which he pleaded</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
GUILTY</hi>.—<hi rend="italic">
